::Spears::

She stood there and didn't move.  She didn't want to turn Striker 
over.  She looked at Prebon and then at Savage.  She couln't get onto 
Savage while carring Striker.  She set Striker down and got on the 
back of Savage.  She put her arms around Prebon and held on. "I am 
sorry, I cannot accomplish both commands, commander."

She let a single tear roll down her face as she looked at Striker. 
She couldn't disobey Tamron, no matter how hard she tried.

Spears, 
> get on the back and hold your lover tight. We're going back to 
base. 
> Anyone who follows will join Spears!"
